    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SINGLEPLAYER MODE:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入一片古老森林的黑暗荒野，直面隐藏在其中考验你的恶魔。你的任务很明确：收集恶魔藏在这片生机盎然、仿佛呼吸的森林深处的秘密圣杯。但是请注意，这片森林绝非普通之地。这里由恶魔掌控，他们被诅咒，拥有将你传送到其他地方的能力——而圣杯正是他们使用的工具！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>目标很清晰：找到所有圣杯！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339100/extras/30193c10d0595172efea744fd978a74c.poster.avif?t=1761659483\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339100/extras/30193c10d0595172efea744fd978a74c.webm?t=1761659483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339100/extras/30193c10d0595172efea744fd978a74c.mp4?t=1761659483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但通向目标的道路充满了危险。首先，你必须面对黑暗领域，那些黑暗似乎拥有生命的阴森之地。在那里，恐怖等待着你，只有无比坚定的耐心才能让你战胜恶魔。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这些夜间的生物会竭尽全力让你偏离道路。但请记住：如果你保持坚韧并抵挡住它们的攻击，它们的抵抗终将减弱。只有在那一刻，它们才会无意中显露隐藏的圣杯——并无意中为你的进步铺路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339100/extras/904f874f8eb8d37aae39d991a05fe879.poster.avif?t=1761659483\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339100/extras/904f874f8eb8d37aae39d991a05fe879.webm?t=1761659483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339100/extras/904f874f8eb8d37aae39d991a05fe879.mp4?t=1761659483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了防卫，你拥有两个重要工具：一把忠实的手枪保护你，以及一只能照亮无尽黑暗的手电筒。明智地使用它们，因为黑暗是狡诈的，而恶魔毫不留情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你展现出力量与耐心，圣杯最终将属于你——它们是你坚持不懈的勇气与决心的奖杯。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339100/extras/2b2fa13be544d0d5958b4b9a0d0c825f.poster.avif?t=1761659483\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339100/extras/2b2fa13be544d0d5958b4b9a0d0c825f.webm?t=1761659483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339100/extras/2b2fa13be544d0d5958b4b9a0d0c825f.mp4?t=1761659483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在我问你：你准备好接受恶魔的挑战并夺回圣杯了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MULTIPLAYER MODE:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>暗影狩猎：圣杯的诅咒</strong><br>投身于1-4玩家的惊悚合作恐怖冒险。寻找所有钥匙以解除圣杯的诅咒，每轮面对一个拥有独特致命能力的新恶魔。使用手电筒穿透黑暗，但要小心：光亮会吸引某些生物。隐藏自己，保持安静，与团队合作逃脱。你会打破诅咒，还是成为下一个受害者？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特点：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动态恶魔，拥有不同能力</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最多4人合作游戏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黑暗且氛围浓厚的环境</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战略性隐藏与资源管理</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>恶魔洪流：阿克萨的最后一战</strong><br>在这款1-4玩家的激烈合作射击游戏中，抵御无尽的恶魔浪潮，保卫阿克萨城。选择致命武器库——从手枪到霰弹枪——对抗愈加残暴的敌人。每波敌人都会提升挑战难度，直到你面对地狱领主。团队合作是生存的关键。你会拯救阿克萨，还是坠入深渊？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特点：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最多4人合作行动</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多样化的武器库</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不断升级的恶魔浪潮与史诗级Boss战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强调团队合作与战术玩法</p></li></ul>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 阿拉伯语, 简体中文, 印度尼西亚语, 日语, 韩语, 波兰语, 俄语, 土耳其语<strong>*</strong>, 乌克兰语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
